= Preface

_This document contains the notes for the Autonomous Robots and Agents course,
taught by Professor Nicola Basilico in the academic year 2025/2026. The notes
follow the course topics, with additional material taken from the recommended
books. They are not intended as a replacement for in-person lectures, as topics
may change over time, but should be used as study aids. Notes were taken by
master's students Alessandro Bordonali and Giovanni Novati, and were reviewed
and approved by Professor Nicola Basilico._
